    "__ env / timeout / nohup / time intentionally NOT single-word safe __",
    "__ (they are transparent wrappers — see _INTERPRETER_WRAPPERS in __",
    "__  pretool_safety.py. The decision is delegated to the inner __",
    "__  command's safety so env/timeout/nohup cannot hide a __",
    "__  destructive inner like 'env kubectl delete' or __",
    "__  'timeout 5 terraform apply'.) __",

    "__ Network __",
    "curl", "wget",

    "__ Modern CLI tools __",
    "eza", "bat", "repomix",

    "__ Shell builtins and meta __",
