    "function", "{", "}",
    "pushd", "popd", "setopt", "history", "alias", "unalias",
    ":", "hash", "help", "ulimit", "umask", "builtin",
    "__ Meta-execution builtins intentionally NOT single-word safe __",
    "__ (eval, exec, source/., command — they run their string arg as __",
    "__  code, defeating interpreter-flag detection. They are still in __",
    "__  the wrapper list so 'env exec python -c' is peeled correctly.) __",

    "__ Shell flow-control keywords __",
    "for", "do", "done", "while", "until",
